Title: Element content of seedlings from seed and liverwort plant tissue in Apollo 15 and Apollo 16 post-flight biomedical evaluations (MMP 21243, MMP 21242)
Description: Element content of seedlings from from seed and liverwort tissue in Apollo 15 and Apollo 16 post-flight biomedical evaluations (MMP 21243, MMP 21242). These findings are related to the feasibility of using plants for food in an international lunar base.
